    "description": {
      "value": "<p>At 20th level, as a bonus action, you can emanate an aura of sunlight. You gain the following benefits for 1 hour:</p><ul><li>Bright light shines from you in a 30-foot radius, and dim light shines 30 feet beyond that. This light is considered daylight.</li><li>Whenever an enemy creature starts its turn in or ends its turn in the bright light, the creature takes 10 radiant damage separately.</li><li>For the duration, you have advantage on saving throws against spells.</li></ul><p>Once you use this bonus action, you cannot use it again until you finish a long rest, unless you expend a 5th-level spell slot to use it again.</p>",
